en: I'm glad there's someone else out there who thinks as highly of you as I do.
I’d really like to keep seeing you, let’s organize another date night soon?
You and Meredith get on well. I can totally see you two together.
Thinking about it makes [wave amp=20 freq=10]me[/wave] want to kiss you.
And I think I just got a great song idea! I’ll sing it to you on our next date?
